                <note rend="inline" type="source">856d.6363/10: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in the Netherlands</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Phillips</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1920-08-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 18, 1920</hi>
                        </date>[<hi rend="italic">—1 p.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>535. Your telegram 212 August 12, 6 p.m.</p>
                <p>You may defer answer to Foreign Office until you receive views of Department
                    which will probably await further information from East Indies and from
                    Secretary of Interior.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Colby</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
